name: Morganne16
author: Morganne
description:
This
 is my first 16 color palette, I've been working on it for a few weeks. 
My goal was a palette capable of emulating the basic colors of the 
rainbow, a few skintones, and the ability to be used for many types of 
artwork. I don't know if I succeded but I'm happy with where it is at 
currently.
